Backend URL Endpoints

Base host:
http://127.0.0.1:8000

Admin
- GET /admin/

Auth
- POST /api/auth/login/
- POST /api/auth/logout/
- POST /api/auth/refresh/
- GET /api/auth/me/
- POST /api/auth/change-password/

Users
- GET /api/users/
- POST /api/users/
- GET /api/users/<int:pk>/
- PATCH /api/users/<int:pk>/
- DELETE /api/users/<int:pk>/

Documents / Search / Metrics / Auditors
- GET /api/health/
- HEAD /api/health/
- POST /api/upload/
- POST /api/search/internal/
- POST /api/search/external/
- POST /api/auditor/verify/
- POST /api/auditor/rotate-key/
- GET /api/auditor/<int:auditor_id>/logs/
- GET /api/auditor/<int:auditor_id>/logs/download/
- GET /api/metrics/internal/
- HEAD /api/metrics/internal/
- GET /api/metrics/external/
- POST /api/auditor/create/
- DELETE /api/auditor/<int:auditor_id>/delete/
- GET /api/auditor/<int:auditor_id>/download/
- GET /api/auditor/<int:id>/
- PATCH /api/auditor/<int:id>/update/
- PUT /api/auditor/<int:id>/update/
- PATCH /api/auditor/<int:id>/status/
- GET /api/auditors/
- POST /api/auditors/
- GET /api/auditors/<int:id>/
- PATCH /api/auditors/<int:id>/
- PUT /api/auditors/<int:id>/
- DELETE /api/auditors/<int:id>/
- POST /api/auditors/<int:id>/rotate-key/
- GET /api/auditors/<int:id>/credentials/

Notes
- `/api/health/` and `/api/metrics/internal/` both implement `HEAD` in addition to `GET`.
- The auditor routes are duplicated in two styles: legacy `/api/auditor/...` paths and REST-style `/api/auditors/...` paths.
- `TokenRefreshView` is provided by `rest_framework_simplejwt`.
